My friend Henry Ault [https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkMGOhCAMhp9mOBqB=
gnrgMNlks9mXMAgdh4yCi3WNb784HjZp2jRN-_f_nCUcUz7MklZiZ-rpWNBE3NcJiTCzbcXcB2-=
