le=3D"color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">Fount</a></strong>.&nbsp=
;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin=
: 0 0 1em 0;">The last time we&#8217;d spoken before I listened to that pod=
cast, <a href=3D"https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkEFuhDAMRU8zWaJgEmAWW=
