?&nbsp;</strong></p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-heigh=
t: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">$5,000 per month.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: =
#1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">No, sorry,=
 that&#8217;s not <em>my</em> answer.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; =
font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;"><strong>$5,000 per =
month is how much clients </strong><em><strong>pay Fount</strong></em><stro=
ng> to run experiments on them and collect their data</strong>. Happily. (I=
t drops to $1,000 per month after the three-month onboarding period.)</p><p=
 style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1=
em 0;">Because Fount&#8217;s data collection mechanism is a <strong>world-c=
lass concierge wellness and performance coaching program</strong> developed=
